//Receta 1 Grilled Chicken Salad A light and healthy salad with grilled chicken breast.
Chicken breast 2 pieces
Lettuce 1 cup
Cherry tomatoes 10 pieces
Cucumber 1/2 piece
Olive oil 2 tablespoons
Grill the chicken breast until fully cooked. Chop the lettuce, tomatoes, and cucumber. Mix all ingredients in a bowl. Drizzle with olive oil and serve.
