//Receta 11 Yogurt Parfaits A delicious and nutritious snack that is perfect for any time of day.
Yogurt 1 cup
Granola 1/2 cup
Fruit, chopped 1/2 cup
In a glass or bowl, layer the yogurt, granola, and fruit. Repeat layers until the glass or bowl is full. Enjoy!
//Receta 12 Trail Mix A filling and satisfying snack that is perfect for a hike or picnic.
Nuts 1 cup
Dried fruit 1 cup
Seeds 1/2 cup
Chocolate chips 1/4 cup
In a bowl, combine the nuts, dried fruit, seeds, and chocolate chips. Mix well and enjoy!
